high_descs: Turn left and walk forward a bit to the middle cabinet of the set of three.
Remove the cardboard box from the cabinet.
Go to the lamp on the left.
anns.task_desc: Hold a cardboard box up to a lit lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the cabinet.
Take the box from the cabinet.
Turn around and go near the floor lamp.
Put the box near the floor lamp and it will be glow.
anns.task_desc: Placed the box near the floor lamp and it will be glow.

high_descs: Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the cabinet.
Pick up box from the cabinet.
After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Moving box from one location to another.
